        "1.Sample Space (𝛀): 𝛀 = \\{0, 1, 2, 3\\}\n",
        "\n",
        "σ algebra ($\\mathfrak{F}$):\n",
        "since this is a finite discrete case,there are $2^4$ = 16 possible subsets of outcomes\n",
        "\n",
        "Probability Measure (P):\n",
        "P(X=3) = 1 - (0.50 + 0.30 + 0.15) = 1 - 0.95 = 0.05\n"
